  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765214093\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765214093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765214093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/c14b3d1fdd524a87fb0f02e023b2631d.avif?t=1765214093\" width=610 height=131 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Features of the game: <br></li><li>You have to jump a lot <br></li><li>Shoot your opponents a lot <br></li><li>Lifting in up <br></li><li>Below you will find red hot spikes moving up <br></li><li>It's raining on the level </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/869844b639e5de3351af6b7eb9aedb35.poster.avif?t=1765214093\" width=594 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/869844b639e5de3351af6b7eb9aedb35.webm?t=1765214093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564950/extras/869844b639e5de3351af6b7eb9aedb35.mp4?t=1765214093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>The main character is a frog that can jump, shoot and teleport! Who is the main enemy of the frog? Perch, yes perch! But the perch cannot come to the surface. Dangerous mechanical robots under the control of a perch are placed on the level, and a special danger is coming from below!",
